docs.lead_paragraph: Who really honors work and liberty? Probably not the 1 percent or the Republican Party.
docs.abstract: Paul Krugman Op-Ed column criticizes Republicans for claiming that the voluntary reduction of working hours by workers due to the health care reform deprives people of the dignity of work; calls it silly to suggest workers can have equal dignity despite huge inequality in pay; maintains the health care reform law will give workers exactly the kind of dignity and freedom Republican politicians pretend to love.
